      "body": "> \"apt-get install -y libboost-dev\"\r\n\r\nThis won't work, because it wont install Boost System. Our [docs](https://github.com/bitcoin/bitcoin/blob/master/doc/build-unix.md#dependency-build-instructions) list the required boost dependencies: `libboost-system-dev libboost-filesystem-dev libboost-test-dev libboost-thread-dev`. You should actually install them if you're trying to build Bitcoin Core.\r\n\r\nIn any case, now that you're running into issues following instructions that are not in this repository, please don't open issues here.",
